    "body": "On Linux or POSIX OSes make_preferred() does nothing, so no harm here. On Windows, I as a Windows user really hate Log-Files or whatever, which display a POSIX style file-path, even if it's supported. What would Linux users think, if there were backslashes in path-names ;)?\n",
